						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the satra on the road to the railway station.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1792, Pramōdūta, Jyēshṭha śu. 15,</hi> corresponding to 1870 A.D., June 13, Monday.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a <hi rend="italic">dharmaśāla</hi> in Veṅkaṭēśvara temple by Veṅkaṭamma, daughter of Rāmanna and the wife of Erikala-reḍḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
